WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:01.450
Karl has five siblings.

00:01.500 --> 00:04.500
His three younger siblings go to a 
 primary school like him.

00:04.500 --> 00:09.833
His two older brothers are unemployed, 
 but are involved in the Socialist Workers' Youth.

00:09.833 --> 00:12.167
Karl's father is a member of the 
 Social Democratic Party

00:12.167 --> 00:15.167
and often attends party events 
 after a hard day's work.

00:15.500 --> 00:17.500
Karl's mother supports the union.

00:17.500 --> 00:21.500
In addition to her work, she takes care of the household 
 and looks after his grandmother.
